Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:07.56,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1815,959.019)\fad(650,650)}「我和妹妹和虚拟空间和」其二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一款游戏想让老师体验一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是之前篡改大家记忆的危险机器吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,已经改良过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会像上次那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且就相信你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么要选我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为就只有老师你一个最合适了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,最合适？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你玩了后就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这次在体验之前 你可要如实交代玩的到底是什么游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,当然会的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这次的游戏是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在各种设定的场景中 让玩家帮助妹妹的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助妹妹的游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏开始后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,玩家化身为男主人公去帮助妹妹的动作游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 游戏会强行读取玩家的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,把游戏内所有角色都换成玩家熟悉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还强行读取
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉会对我的大脑有什么影响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你说这么多遍没事 我反而觉得更有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那就开始游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘记说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不把妹妹成功救出的话 是退出不了游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还请加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是凉花吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,凉花 没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老师和妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是阿嘿剪刀手老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,来玩游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很简单的游戏来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只要向我展示你俩兄妹之间的羁绊 就算成功逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这个女人因为会妨碍你俩的兄妹情谊 所以我把她杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为这样的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我来说明游戏规则
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,游戏开始后在规定时间内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,把包包里装的衣服让妹妹穿上就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,必须你亲自给她穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,若是她自己穿的话就算失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 游戏开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快把我的衣服脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你突然让我这么做 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我很害羞的 快给我穿上好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不把内衣脱了的话 看来是穿不上的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 这种事我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快点帮我脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起从这里逃出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快点脱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,脱自己妹妹的内裤 我真的做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 就当是为了我 脱下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救妹妹失败
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,GAME OVER了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,移动到下一个场景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 同伴 听得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,听得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你那边如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子他们在某处安装了炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,准备让这栋大楼灰飞烟灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这种事情 我绝对不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那就交给你了 伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 烦人的爬虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还在做无畏的挣扎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在没有将你菊花用铅球塞满之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,大言不惭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你宝贵的妹妹还在我的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,凉花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不想你妹妹受伤的话 就别妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来阴的 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,祐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,凉花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上救你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不然的话你宝贵的妹妹就得死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,区区拜金小毛贼居然敢对我的妹妹下手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是追到地狱的尽头 我也要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是有本事的话 就来阻止我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,输给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我来当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,把凉花放了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,凉花 躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你别以为这样就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在你妹妹身上安放了个特殊的炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,解除的方法是让你妹妹高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,其体内设置的数值达到峰值后就能解除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我劝你还是不要强拆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你拆的那一瞬间就会马上爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你能让你的妹妹高潮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是感谢你的热心解说啊 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么又是这样惨死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,摸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,摸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,凉花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两人一起活着出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么上不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,凉花 你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我想直接感受哥哥的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,凉花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哥…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,达到峰值了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,计时器还没停下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,请按下终止按钮进行解除操作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,居然还有终止按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,终止按钮就在你妹妹的乳峰上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,顺带一说 不直接触摸的话是无效的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,直接接触？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是哥哥的话 我不会介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,凉花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹成功救出 返回现实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 老师真是大胆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 凉花 你不是出门了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个 哥哥 果然是喜欢巨乳的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不是的 我应该是正在摸你的胸才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的…
